Azaadi VPN is committed to protecting the privacy and security of our users. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect our users' data, and demonstrates our dedication to ensuring the highest level of security and privacy for our users.

Information Collection and Use
We collect the following information from our users:
IP address and country (For selecting nearest server from your location)

We use this information solely for the purpose of:
Providing and improving our VPN services
Restoring user purchases
Maintaining and optimizing our servers
Enhancing user experience and app performance

We do not collect any other personal data, browsing history, or sensitive information. Our primary goal is to ensure our users' online security and privacy.

Data Security and Protection
Our top priority is to ensure the security and privacy of our users' data. We implement robust security measures to protect user data, including:
Encryption to protect user data
Secure servers to store data
No logs maintenance on servers

In the event of a data breach from our database, we will:
Immediately investigate and contain the breach
Notify affected users and relevant authorities within 72 hours
Take prompt action to mitigate the breach and prevent future occurrences

User Rights and Consent
By using our app, users agree to our privacy policy and terms of use. We will:
Obtain user consent before collecting any data
Allow users to request data deletion at any time
Provide users with clear information about our data collection and usage practices
Ensure users' rights to access, correct, and delete their personal data

Terms of Use
Azaadi VPN Terms of Use
Acceptance
By downloading and using our app, you agree to these terms of use and our privacy policy.

User Obligations
Use our app for lawful purposes only
Not attempt to reverse-engineer or compromise our app's security
Comply with our privacy policy and terms of use
Not use our app for malicious or fraudulent activities

Dispute Management
In the event of a dispute arising from our app's usage, we will:
Attempt to resolve the dispute through negotiation and mediation
Follow the laws and regulations of the user's country of residence
Seek arbitration if necessary

Changes
We reserve the right to modify our privacy policy and terms of use at any time. Users will be notified of significant changes through our app or email communication.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy or terms of use, please contact us at inbox.dev@proton.me.

By using our app, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to our privacy policy and terms of use.
